➜《黄帝内经》：亥寝鸣天鼓，寅兴漱玉津；“气是续命芝，津是延年药”
http://www.sohu.com/a/194656857_99989330	14364
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20171001/26f168d5e53b4db286baa7157cedc716.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">刘先银题写书名《黄帝内经的生命智慧》</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170928/a908eaf4e6a748f48cbed54395bff4d6.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">刘先银题写书名《和光同尘》</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20171001/d073900f5ea6402c966fc17dd8c5a500.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20171001/70a60cd46d5f4679a0e70e9e2bca820c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
